				<td colspan="2"><span>I don't even think they are fun.
<br />

<br />
I can understand the desire for the Barbie Mask.
<br />

<br />
I can understand someone with more money than sense shelling out big bucks for the gnome mask.  When your gear is all no drop, what else are you gonna do with the plat?
<br />

<br />
I can understand doing the DE mask camp as it is a rite of passage and can come in handy getting your OT hammer.
<br />

<br />
I cannot understand camping the peck mask.  Its a epic level camp that gives you nothing but an illusion.
<br />

<br />
Perhaps it was my Raster of Guk camping experience that made me never want to go into the bowels of some old world dungeon and sit on my a$ for countless hours on some elusive mob. 
